version: 0.19
date:    Sun Oct  1 10:05:13 CST 2006
changes:
- Recognize whitespace after the heredoc marker, e.g. "<< 'FOO'"
- Don't treat a literal '<<' string by itself as a heredoc marker.
- Don't treat '<<=' as a heredoc marker.
- Support 'use_means_now'.

